# Crypto Trading Bot with AI & Telegram Integration

## Features
- 24/7 trading signal bot for Binance and Coinbase.
- AI model using TensorFlow learns from your trades to improve signals.
- Telegram commands:
  - /signal - Get general trade signal
  - /signal.s - Get short-term trade signal
  - /signal.l - Get long-term trade signal
  - #trade_id - Confirm a trade you entered (e.g., #123)
  - /help - command list
- Tracks confirmed trades in SQLite database.
- Self-learning with periodic model retraining.

## Setup Instructions

1. Clone or download the repository.

2. Create a virtual environment and activate it:

```bash
python3.13 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/macOS
venv\\Scripts\\activate  # Windows
